hopobject.body: Can I use your phone? onrush rx reviews This gorgeous dress is by Marc Jacobs and is from his AW13 collection. The emerald hue is stunning and the sequins lift this simple dress into glamorous territory. And with its skimpy straps and very low back it's still a really sexy look. It just goes to show that you can look classy, beautiful and sexy without resorting to thongs, PVC hotpants and disturbingly raunchy photo shoots.
